: "", "twitter": "", "created": 1458024699, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b75f/9ee0/163414_mini.png?m=1574570790", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b75f/9ee0/163414_mini.png?m=1574570790", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 163414}, "last_reply_by": "huihuiHK", "last_touched": 1626399948, "title": "大家在 Linux 服务器上会配置那些 alias 提升效率？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/789686", "created": 1626326665, "content": "先说我的（公司）：\r\nalias cp=\"cp -i\"\r\nalias rm=\"rm -i\"\r\nalias mv=\"mv -i\"\r\nalias ll=\"ls -l --color=auto\"\r\n...", "content_rendered": "<p>先说我的（公司）：\nalias cp=\"cp -i\"\nalias rm=\"rm -i\"\nalias mv=\"mv -i\"\nalias ll=\"ls -l --color=auto\"\n...</p>\n", "last_modified": 1626326665, "replies": 56, "id": 789686}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1615111905", "name": "iphone", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1615111905", "title": "iPhone", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone", "topics": 8617, "footer": "这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。", "header": "Say hello to the future.", "title_alternative": "iPhone", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1615111905", "stars": 2689, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 8, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"username": "youthfire", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8760/d018/33111_mini.png?m=1562138890", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/youthfire", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1359250777, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8760/d018/33111_mini.png?m=1562138890", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8760/d018/33111_mini.png?m=1562138890", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 33111}, "last_reply_by": "pcmgr456", "last_touched": 1626367054, "title": "咸鱼的官方手机回收可以不用相信了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/789657", "created": 1626319183, "content": "基本上每次出新代前都会把旧手机回收，以前都是用爱回收（ iPhone5 时期），大概从 2018 年左右开始用咸鱼，因为价格会比爱回收多 200-300 元，实际体验很好。这次出 iPhoneX 256g，又特意对比了下，同时 app 和现场都对比了。\r\n\r\n爱回收的 app 报价 1660 （ 1600+60 补贴），因为有说现场会给多一些，还特意去了两家线下实体店，报价一致。期间还去闪修侠打听了，说和爱回收一样价格。\r\n\r\n咸鱼报价 2500 （挂售），直接回收 2200 。app 虽然标支持上海直接上门，但换了 3 个地址都说不支持，只能顺丰。\r\n\r\n之前上 v 站看了咸鱼挂售的坑，所以也就不考虑，只选择直接回收。心想，就算被刀，600 元差价应该也够了。结果今天电话通知，说回收 1300，我直接拒绝让寄回。\r\n\r\n总之，大家如果在爱回收和咸鱼之间犹豫回收，亲身体验下来，不用考虑咸鱼了。目前只希望寄回来的手机不要有什么问题。", "content_rendered": "<p>基本上每次出新代前都会把旧手机回收，以前都是用爱回收（ iPhone5 时期），大概从 2018 年左右开始用咸鱼，因为价格会比爱回收多 200-300 元，实际体验很好。这次出 iPhoneX 256g，又特意对比了下，同时 app 和现场都对比了。</p>\n<p>爱回收的 app 报价 1660 （ 1600+60 补贴），因为有说现场会给多一些，还特意去了两家线下实体店，报价一致。期间还去闪修侠打听了，说和爱回收一样价格。</p>\n<p>咸鱼报价 2500 （挂售），直接回收 2200 。app 虽然标支持上海直接上门，但换了 3 个地址都说不支持，只能顺丰。</p>\n<p>之前上 v 站看了咸鱼挂售的坑，所以也就不考虑，只选择直接回收。心想，就算被刀，600 元差价应该也够了。结果今天电话通知，说回收 1300，我直接拒绝让寄回。</p>\n<p>总之，大家如果在爱回收和咸鱼之间犹豫回收，亲身体验下来，不用考虑咸鱼了。目前只希望寄回来的手机不要有什么问题。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1626319183, "replies": 48, "id": 789657}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_large.png?m=1620805836", "name": "wechat", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_normal.png?m=1620805836", "title": "微信", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/wechat", "topics": 2681, "footer": "", "header": "关于微信及微信小程序的讨论节点", "title_alternative": "WeChat", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_mini.png?m=1620805836", "stars": 435, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 649, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"username": "zshstc", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c5b0/3cd6/193770_mini.png?m=1585823222", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zshstc", "tagline": "", "twitter": "zshleon", "created": 1474990040, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c5b0/3cd6/193770_mini.png?m=1585823222", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c5b0/3cd6/193770_mini.png?m=1585823222", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 193770}, "last_reply_by": "xz410236056", "last_touched": 1626379387, "title": "微信终于可以电脑端