ex.com/go/macos", "topics": 16847, "footer": "<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1607656854", "stars": 4357, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "jiaslbang", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/37de/d539/43954_mini.png?m=1625036117", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jiaslbang", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1376564614, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/37de/d539/43954_mini.png?m=1625036117", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/37de/d539/43954_mini.png?m=1625036117", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 43954}, "last_reply_by": "hd2ex", "last_touched": 1626356373, "title": "Mac 下 Logitech Options 的自定义配置经常失效，变成平平无奇的普通蓝牙状态，有啥好办法吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/789658", "created": 1626319214, "content": "- 鼠标：Anywhere 2S\r\n- OS：用过 Catalina/Big Sur，都经常发生\r\n\r\n## 1 、常见的场景是\r\n去开会，把 Mac 带走，回工位，连上鼠标，鼠标上的自定义按键就没反应了\r\n\r\n## 2 、摸索出的临时解决办法如下，但每次都走一遍就很麻烦\r\n打开蓝牙面板，主动断开鼠标连接，然后按一下鼠标，在搜索蓝牙设备里找到，重新连接", "content_rendered": "<ul>\n<li>鼠标：Anywhere 2S</li>\n<li>OS：用过 Catalina/Big Sur，都经常发生</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>1 、常见的场景是</h2>\n<p>去开会，把 Mac 带走，回工位，连上鼠标，鼠标上的自定义按键就没反应了</p>\n<h2>2 、摸索出的临时解决办法如下，但每次都走一遍就很麻烦</h2>\n<p>打开蓝牙面板，主动断开鼠标连接，然后按一下鼠标，在搜索蓝牙设备里找到，重新连接</p>\n", "last_modified": 1626319214, "replies": 35, "id": 789658}]